attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KSYbmn3OQjFF06TjIOf_display_text
attribs.current: When ever the black knight takes at least 20 slashing damage from a single melee weapon attack roll a d20 on a 1-10 nothing happens on an 11-15 the knight loses a leg if he has any left on a 16-20 one arm is severed if he has any left if a player attempts to cut off his head when attacking and the damage dealt is at least 20 rol a d20 on a 17-20 the knight is successfully decapitated and his hp immediatly drops to 0

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KSYcVmCWNDNvc5kM75Y_name
attribs.current: Alright well call it a draw

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KSYcVmCWNDNvc5kM75Y_display_text
attribs.current: When the black knight is reduced to 0mmhe does not die as normal instead he is incapacitated immobilized and able o talk but unable to move when immobilised in this way the Black knight canno regen hp and must rest for 1d days in order to grow back any lost limbs and return to full health any lost limbs regrow in the order they were removed  takeing 1d8+4 hours each to be fully functional again beginning after the 1d4 days of rest once the knight has successfully rested and regained all lost limbs he may begin to regen hp again as normal

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KSYd4AuHGP0DDuod3Km_display_text
attribs.current: If the Black knight sucessfully regen bak to full health he will immediatly seek out the  to find the creature that dealt the incapacitatiing blow demanding a rematch the black knight knows where the charater is and will always arrive 1d4 weeks after leaving to seek out his opponet regardless of where the creature is in the world often with MOnty Python Holy grail overture playing to precede his arrival he will respond with any question as to how he got there with an intiative roll  if he appears during a combat encouner  the Knight will join the fight and if the chracter dies to someone else the black knight will hunt them instead  The black knight will coninue  to gloat and mock them mercilisslyuntil his head is removed and buried underground for 24 hours. or unil his target admits hes the victor
